\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You say your father was a wheelwright?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 A wheel - joiner and wheelwright, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you know where he came from, was he a Bolton man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 A Bolton man, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about your mother, was she a Bolton woman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, she was a Bolton woman, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And your father was always a wheelwright?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. No was always - always - a joiner and wheelwright.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He never did any part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he was all - he worked at one place for fifty years. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your mother work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh mother was hard}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  woman. She worked at home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You mean looking after you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Looking after - she made shirts as - she was a shirt maker at home on - on the - on the sewing machine and - she - she made three pounds a week making shirts at ninepence a dozen. Yes, she used be up at four o'clock in the morning 'til eleven at night.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Even after she'd had you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes, lovely - lovely person she was my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You're fond of your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She was easy to talk to was she?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. She wanted - she w
anted - she worked - she worked - she worked for us, she wanted us - she wanted us - she wanted to see us - well off. She worked and saved the money. She'd no need to work, my father's was a good job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But she saved it for you to give you a start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was your father easy to talk to or was he Victorian?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Me father was a very hard working man. I never knew - I never knew him to have a Sat'day and - a Sat'day and a Sunday off. He worked every Sat'day afternoon and - and Sunday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was he easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, a nice man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Could you share your troubles with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. I had two extraordinary parents, nobody had better. Oh, he was hard working man. Both my father and mother was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When your mother was working she was at home to look after you wasn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 she
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where I was born? I was born at 144 Manchester Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You lived there all your life did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I lived there - and then we - we removed farther down to 286 Manchester Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So you always lived on Manchester Road as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, I - I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 from Manchester - Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where did you live the longest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I lived the longest at 286 Manchester Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why did you just move further along the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well, you see - we wanted a bigger house, you see, and - my father bought - he - he had some houses - he - he worked hard all his life and he - he wasn't without money and he had some property built. You see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This was a result of working weekends of course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Yes. And - you see, he were a very - he was like the boss at the place where he - it was a bleachworks you see and they to do a lot of work when the place was 
finished. They had - they had to work weekends to keep the place going. You see. And - they bought - he helped to bring a patent out at the - the works where he worked at and - and it worked - four - four - it worked fourteen years night and day without s
topping. He helped to bring a patent out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What was the patent for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Cloth - cloth, it was called the Warburton finish - W.Finish it was called. Fin - finish - special finish on cloth, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did it give it a shine or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It just gave it a nice finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where you lived at 288 how many rooms were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 286. Oh yes, there was - well it was a big house, there was - four bedrooms. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And just your family lived there, did you have anyone else, relatives or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. Just our family there that was all, the family.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you use the rooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Dinner - dining room, yes. It was four room upstairs and four rooms down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So you'd have plenty of room for sleeping arrangements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. No. The boys room - in one room, see. And two girls in another. Mother, father in another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh she were a grand cook. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember where she cooked and what type of range she used?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh she used the ordinary - ordinary - ordinary oven. Range. The old fashioned range you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The black leaded one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. She always had an - an oxtail in th'oven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oxtail was your favourite was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh my father liked oxtail soup - he liked oxtail soup you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And she used to leave it in the oven stewing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, stewing, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she ever have any paid help in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. Well I had two sisters you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she do her own washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did all her own washing and made all those shirts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How about your father, did he mend your shoes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh no. No, no, he was always at his work.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your mother also make your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, oh no, never made any clothes. Only made shirts, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You always bought your clothes did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember where they were bought and when what time of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well we always had them for the sermons at - at the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was this Whit Week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, our sermons were always on the Second Sunday in May.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you always had new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you always had them for then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And - me father didn't like new something - new clothes - new clothes coming into house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He - he could put you what - you could put a cow on the table but he didn't like new clothes coming into the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was he superstitious about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he - they had - me - me sister had to hide them away and when they used to bring them out he - they used say
, oh, we've had these months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He didn't like them buying new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, didn't buy - buying new clothes, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It's unusual isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was it because he was a keen saver do you think or something like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well he was a very careful man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But they were always new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He didn't like new clothes coming in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But you always had them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh we always had them at the sermons time, you know, for - always for the second Sunday in May.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were they new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Used to buy new ones. Never bought second hand ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your dad help in the home at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Never?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Never did decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, no, he never did no decorating. No, he were busy at his work you see he started at s
ix - used to work at - start six o'clock in the morning you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What time did he finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Half past five at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 That was a long day, and Saturday and Sunday too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well he - he used to work Sat'day afternoons and - Sunday mornings. He was - he used to work 'til dinner time at Sunday - every week.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you see a lot of your father, did he help undress you or put you to bed or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh no. No, no, none at all, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did he take you out at all without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
No, he - he never took us out much, mother took us out a lot. Mother - she didn't go out a lot. I used to help with - on a Saturday - Sat'day night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where did you go, shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 We used to go shopping, yes. And we - she would stand on - on - on - on Victoria - on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 Nelson}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  Square listening to Salvation Army.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This is in Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You liked going shopping with your mother did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But your dad you didn't see much of with working long hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he was working - working late. He always - he was always working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Did you have jobs to do as children in the house, did you help each other as children the younger help the older and the older help the young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - you see - me eldest sister and me eldest brot
her they was one - you see. Very close. And I was very close with the - me other sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You felt very close to her did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, well - we - we backed one another up you know in the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You mean if there was a fight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well we never fought but you understand she always took - I used to take her side and she used to take my side. You see. Very close, yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you do jobs about the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I never did any jobs about the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But the sisters did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The sisters did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What did they do, help your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Help me mother. Help me mother.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 With the housework?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Oh yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you boys never did anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I don't - no, I had two sisters do you see, well I had three understand
 but one died you see, her name was Nellie, she died young. I think about fourteen I think when she died you see. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So the boys had quite a good time while the girls worked in the house did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they - house you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Had you to go to bed at a certain time in those days and what time did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Not even when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, we never - was to time to go to bed. Mother didn't like us being out late at night and she would - she would - she would never g
o to bed until was all in. We never had a key, she wouldn't give us a key.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Even when you were growing older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were growing up, no, I never had a key. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She always waited up for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Always waited up. Never had a key, none of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you never had to go to bed early when you were at school even?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I - we wasn't up very late but if I went out - we came home late she wouldn't - se never had a key to get in with. She always -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who put you to bed as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What position were you in the family, you weren't the baby by any chance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I was 1 year younger than me.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This was the sister who died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 My mother - my mother worked hard. She never - she always used to say that work never killed anybody, it was worry. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But she didn't have a lot of worry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh no, no, she'd }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 no worry}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 . She was - she used to be working on this }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 sewing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 machine from four o'clock in the morning 'til eleven o'clock at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And she did it all to save for you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. They were all - the shirts was cut out, she only had to stitch them, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She got them from a factory did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh she made - she made them for - for a man as had a business you understand you see, they sold these, was i
n a wholesale business and - she used to make special shirts for him, she used to get eighteenpence for special shirts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 ere}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  special shirts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 People as was very big and - and - what had - they were made - made to measure and - she used to get
 eighteenpence for making one of those you see. But they was all cut out you understand, they only wanted sewing together and - a - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 buttonholing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  and buttons put on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She wouldn't buttonhole them though would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she get extra money for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 buttonholing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, no, ninepence a dozen she used to get. Made three pounds a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she do the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 buttonholing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  by hand too or did she have an attachment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I really couldn't tell you, I think she did it by the machine I think.
 Wheel - wheeler and Wilson sewing machine - it - it earned some money for her. She earned three pounds a week making shirts at ninepence a dozen. You could buy - you could buy shirts - in those days you know, best shirt there was you could buy for half a
 crown you know. You could buy the best shirt there was for half a crown. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So your mother got a very small faction of the cost of the shirt for all her work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did she ever find time to cook or clean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh she never - she did much - she never went out. She - she only went out at Saturday night, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she never have any friends or go out alone at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But she and your father went out together did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they didn't go out much out together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But your father went out did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. He - he only went out one night a week for - for Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did he go to pubs or clubs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he just went in to have a drink. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 To a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But your mother didn't go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She just went out Saturday night and you went with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Take me with her, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And it was always the same place was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, well she used to go and have a drink do you see. And do some shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where would she have a drink, would she be able to go into a pub alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What happened to you while she went in for a drink?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I - used - I used to have a drink too but I didn't drink - she'd have something, a beer or a stout something lik
e that, I used to have a mineral water do you see. But she used to take me with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you always went shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And listening to the Salvation Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your father take part in sport at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he didn't take sport much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did he attend races or have a bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, no, he was a - no, he wouldn't bet. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they belong to any savings clubs, boot clubs or sick clubs, funeral clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. Never - never - never - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about a funeral club, they'd be in insurance wouldn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh she - she was in his own club at his own trades club. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Would that cover the family in event of death or what did it actually do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well it - it - it paid for sick - if he - if he was off ill or sick, see, get so much a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And it was a club belonging to the trade itself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes, the wheel - the joiners and wheelwrights. You don't - you don't hear of any wheelwrights today, they've gone out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What did your father actually do, did he ever talk about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh he was a pass master - he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15432001\charrsid14639786 pastmaster}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  at his work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about wheelwrights?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well they used to make wheels for carts. For the firm he worked at do you see
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And he would just make wheels all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh he -
 he - you see, there - there wasn't motor cars in those days. There was - horse - horse - horse - horses and lorries and they - he worked at this place the bleachworks and he - he used to make - make all the carts and - and - and the wheels for them and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The carts as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Yes. You see. And then at weekends, they used to - have to go into the place you know because - they had - in the firm, you know, it was a bleaching firm and they'd - they had four - what they call fourlers like they come down 
to the cloth you know. Hit the cloth you know - stretched it do you see. The woodwork and they had to - do - these wouldn't last for ever and ever and they had to keep - he had to keep making fresh ones you understand and fixing them in at weekend when th
e place was closed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So this was why he worked weekends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
That's the reason why he worked weekends. You see. You see, they - they put cloth on, it run round rollers you know and you see - by - these dump - coming down on the cloth they were running 
round, fourlers coming down on the cloth dump - they got more yards out of it. It was stretching it all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Surely it would shrink when it was washed wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You see. No, it - you see, that was the idea of it, they got more yards out -
 out of it you see. It might get a - a fifty length of cloth and by time it had gone through the rollers and dumped on and down you know - it - they'd happen get - sixty or seventy yards out of it. Yes, yes, do you see. Of course he had to make - he had t
o make these things for - because they got down on a Sat'day see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But he'd have to pay insurance or something for you children surely, say when your sister died he would need money for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well if he - mother paid that out of her wages. To the insurance man as used to call. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But he wasn't a member of any other clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were young did you share a bedroom with someone else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, I - there was four of - four - four boys and we - we was - were in one of the rooms. Two - two in each bed. Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How about bathing in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh we had a bathroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This was unusual wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, was a bathroom, yes. But we had - the other house, when we - we'd no - no bathroom in the other house, 144. Y
ou see, when we removed to this - 286, you see with a bath in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember how often you had a bath in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh had a bath every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about putting clean clothes on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh used to put clean clothes on every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 At the other house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You see, my mother brought - up in a - in the public house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She came from publicans did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And - they kept the Bull in Badgergate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And - there a man used to stay with them, he was a lion tamer and - he used to come to the Bolton Show of a Christmas time.
