\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Can you tell me if your parents played games with you as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, we'd games in the house, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What kind of games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh, musical chairs and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have a lot of books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they buy books or did you get them from the library in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh we had to buy them you know, not - not many libraries going in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about magazines and papers, did they have those in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Only}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786  the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 - the church magazine. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Just the church magazine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Nothing else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember your father reading out loud or your mother reading out loud or them reading to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, never read to us. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember a funeral in the family and who went and what type of clothes they wore?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 A funeral in the family? Yes, I remember me father being buried and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 That wouldn't be before 1918 though would it? Do you remember any as a child, what about when your sister died, do you remember that?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, don't remember that. No, I - I never remember her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember any relatives dying though when you were a child and what it was like a funeral in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I - only remember me father being buried, that's all. And me mother you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was it a big funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - not - I wouldn't say big, just an ordinary funeral that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who attended?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well mostly the family. I - I - I had a brother home from the war, he just - he got over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Which brother was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Hames. And - he managed to get over on leave and he went back, he was killed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Which brother was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 James.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He was the second boy and he died in the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, oh he blown to smithereens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But you don't remember a funeral at all otherwise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Only father's that's all, and me mother's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Can you tell me how you spent your Saturdays as a child, what did you do on Saturdays? I know you always went to church on Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I was always church at Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you spent Saturdays then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The cricket matches and football matches. See, was interested in football you see. I was a
 bit - I should have been a professional footballer but my father bought this business for me. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 Pawnbroking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 business you see, you see, I started on Falls Road at - in the shop working in a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 pawnbroking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 business and then I got moved up and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This was your first job was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 First job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 That would be interesting in those days wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - if I led me life again I'd be a pawnbroker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It was so interesting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, very interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about it in the days before 1918, ab
out the people who came in and how much the charges were and the type of things they pawned, all this sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - of course - course it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 pawnbroking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  didn't get a very good name you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You always think of a pawnbroker as somebody very hard hearted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, no. No, I never was - I got on in my trade well because I wasn't hard hearted. I used to help them more. Well you see, }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 pawnbroking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  got - I would say - you were looked on as a pawnbroker you was nobody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They thought we was - the scum of the earth and - we was robbers but you see - a different altogether, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 pawnbroking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
s very hard work. You've got a lot of work to do to make any money. You see, you could come to my shop and - and - and - and you could pledge an article for a pound and you could have it in a month and you'd only pay a fivepence interest. That's all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was this after the first war or before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Always been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Before the first world war it was fivepence was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Fivepence in the pound. See.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about why they had to pawn their clothes?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well you see some people, they - they got - they didn't get very much money and you see - a lot of people made themselves - poor by drinking and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 gambling}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 . You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And these were they types that came to the pawn shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
They - them - them were the type but there was some - very - ladies and people come to the pawn shop, must bear in mind, there are people was - you know - what fell on hard times, you see. And there was some very go
od - people, of course people used to come with stuff what they'd stolen you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you know, did you have a policeman cal in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - well we had - we had - the - C.I.D. they used to call 'em, the - private detectives used to co
me to the shop every day and you used to give a list of articles what was stolen, you see. And - we used to have to go through this list and - and - and look, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you ever have stolen articles brought in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, I - I've - I've - I've rung up for the police and called them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you've actually }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 caught}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  the thief?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember any particular case?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - we all used to help - help - help the police because you see ours was a very funny trade to work. You see. It'
s not an easy trade to work in - in - in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 pawnbroking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
, you see, you've so many different class of people to - to - to work with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about the different classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well you see you get some very good people, you get some very poor - bad people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How do you mean bad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - they're - they're people as - how - they gamble and they drink a lot you understand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you get a lot of this in Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was your shop in a very poor district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, in a - a very poor district you see. I used to lend four hundred and fifty pound at Monday. And it was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What year would it be when you were lending this amount?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 About 1930 - 1940.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were a boy where did you work first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I worked in a pawnbrokers on Falls Road. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What did you do as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well s had to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What was your job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I had to - I was learning the trade then you see when I was a young boy. I used to have to make the - the pawn tick
ets out and, you know, anybody came in used to - pawn something I used to have to make the ticket out. They wanted a - a ticket; you understand, a pawn ticket do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 I got it through me parents - this - this sister 
was very close to me, was very friendly with the firm - with the pawn people, you see, and they got me to - he like got me going into this you see but - as I told you before we was very - we backed one another up and she was so keen on me starting in this
 pawnbroking business.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you like it as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh yes, I liked it boy - I - yes, I - I liked it as - you know - as I say I told you about if I'd to live me life again I'd be a pawnbroker. And - and there's none in Bolton now today. There's none. But, you know, I could start tomorrow and make a -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were a boy in pawnbroking you would see a lot of poverty then wouldn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, a lot of poverty, yes, but they made their own poverty. They made their own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why, tell me why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why? Because used to - betting and gambling. Betting and drinking. See.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What would happen, the women would bring the clothes in on Monday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were telling me this woman used to come every Tuesday morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Every Tuesday mo
rning and pledge an article for a pound. And - with my pound she went to the Co-op and spent grocer - spent her money in groceries and she - with that pound she made three shilling off - our of me out of that pound because she got three shillings divi in 
t
he pound, in the Co-op in those days. Happen you don't remember that do you? Three shillings. My pound - I used to make fivepence but out - out of my pound she made three shillings out of my pound, she went to the Co-op and spent it in groceries and she g
ot three shillings divi on that and I made fivepence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And the groceries would be just for her family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Just for her family, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And then she would come and get the article back at the weekend would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did yo
u assess the articles, how would you tell how much they were worth? Before 1918 when people were very poor what type of goods would be brought in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - oh there - the things was better in those days than what they are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, yes, better made. More hand made. Better - better - better quality.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What sort of things would the women bring in to pawn before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - there certain things what were bug bear to a pawnbroker, ladies coats and ladies frocks wasn't good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they went out of fashion quick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did people often leave things on your hands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, yes, we'd things left on our hands. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So you'd have to be sure in assessing an article that you'd covered yourself in case you'd to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 sell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, oh yes. See. But - jewellery was all right you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In a poor district would you ever get jewellery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, we took a lot of jewellery in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What sort of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - you see - a lot of people used come 
from outside districts to come to a pawn - to a pawnbrokers, they didn't like what - people where they lived. We got them from outside, see, miles away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You mean they'd be a better class person would come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And they come with jewellery, you see, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they always redeem it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Sometimes and sometimes they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So you would have to know about jewellery and everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh - oh yes, yes. Well you - you picked that knowledge up. We - we started as a boy, you see, you - you pick it up as you go along.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you serve an apprenticeship for this in your first pawnbrokers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Yes. I worked at a place. And - I about four or five years and then I - and then I moved to another place you see, advert in the paper wanted a - a 
junior and; I went to work for this man but he wasn't big - doing a very big trade because he wasn't a man cut out for business in my opinion, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember what your wage was at the first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh about twelve shillings a week.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 That was good pay wasn't it, did you think it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I didn't call it a big wage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you think it was fair though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I was - I was sixteen or seventeen year old you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, when I went to this other place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was that your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, second.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember what you got at your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well about - about eight - about ten shillings. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What did you do with it, did you give it all to your mum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I really ca
n't tell you, to be honest. But - I went to work at this other place and - he didn't do a big trade. He said it was always funny, I could always do more business when he wasn't in the shop than he could do when he was in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why do you think this was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I suppose his - manner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was he rude or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well it was - take - either take or have it or - you know - wouldn't - was swearing at people, well, you can't do that in business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He used to swear at them, why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - he was a man of that type.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You think he regarded them as inferior the people who brought the things, was it this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well he was a - man - to me, he wasn't cut out - you see, he - his - his wife - his wife - brother was a pawnbroker, you see, his wife's brother and - he hadn't been a pawnbroker understand, he come in - and - he hadn't been brought up to it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What do you think was the most necessary thing for a good pawnbroker, in regard to his treatment of the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh you want to be civil them and - 
and be nice to them. It's always the poor people, you've not got to - you know - you see, because as long as you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 making}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 money out of them, you see, you're dependant on them coming, you see and - and some people wouldn't put up with - with - see and - 
he went to - he went to - he went to Australia went abroad, he - shop was put up for sale and my father bought it. Oh he bought it for me. 'Cos it was no use to him because he wasn't a pawnbroker so - you see, and of course I understood the trade and - it
 was kept in the family, my - my eldest brother went to the croft, he give up the croft and came to work with me. You see, but he - I was really the pawnbroker because he didn't understand it, he had to be trained same as I, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The first job you went to what hours did you work where you were training?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh the shop where I bought we used to open at half past five of a Monday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But the first job you had when you were training to be a pawnbroker, what time did you start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh, about seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What time did you finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you work Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Worked Sat'days 'til eleven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I didn't work Sundays. Not allowed to - you - you're not allowed to work Sundays in a pawnbrokers shop, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have holidays with pay in your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Certain - certain days you can't - you couldn't work Sundays, Good Fridays and - and Sundays, Good Fridays you couldn't work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why Good Fridays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well it's - it's stipulated in the pawnbrokers act. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you get holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Holidays with pay? I don't think so, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you get on with your boss here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 We never had - we never had many holidays in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you get on with your boss at your first job and how did he treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 He was good was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes. It was a - it was a - it was a good sales shop besides a pawnbroking shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They sold something else did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - we - we'd tailors - it was a
 tailors shop besides a pawnbrokers. He - he'd a - he'd a man tailor and two tailoress - girl tailoresses in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And just you and him in the pawn shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he'd another man in - in - in the pawn shop. This firm had three shops. They'd - the
y'd another one at Belgrave Street, up - Bromley Fold and they - they'd - they'd four shops. They'd one at - one at Farnworth and one at Walkden, near - Shipperbothams their name were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you started off by making out the tickets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, making out - out the tickets and - and shifting things you know. Putting things away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Then what did you go on to do after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - I had to do - clean the shop up and - and - help to do the window dressing in the - in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me how you pr
ogressed in your job, you started off by doing the tickets and then you went on to putting things away and then you - how did he teach you gradually the trade, what were the things he taught you to learn the trade of pawnbroking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well he - I had to ma
ke the tickets out. I - we - we entered them into a book. You ask them the name, what's your name. You enter it in. Where do you live? You enter that in - into the book. You see. And - what their pawning, a pair of ladies shoes or pair of }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 means}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  shoes or ma
ns suit, what it was, or a lady's coat and - and then you make the ticket out, you see, put - put their name on and on - and address on the ticket and what it is. A mans suit - twenty shillings lent on, you see, that's -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What would be the next thing you learnt to learn the trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well you - you got to a - estimate a value what - what - they're coming in and might - they might - might ask - bring a pair of shoes in and might ask five shillings on them and say, no, I can't allow you five shillings 
on these, they're not worth five shillings, they're too well worn, you can only have half a crown on them, you see. Some - might take 'em, say, oh no, I - I won't take that, they take them away, see. They might go to another pawnbroker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you get a lot of hard up stories though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Hard up stories, oh aye - oh aye, they tell tale right enough. Well they say they want - wanted money for pay rent you know and - and - and then - old rent man - rent man'd be coming for his money and they - they wanted to pawn for to pay their rent man.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This happened a lot did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You got a lot of hard up stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, hard up stories, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have regular customers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, regular customers, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well they used to come in at one pledge and they used to take 'em out at Friday or Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Mostly clothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Clothing, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What happened - it was left folded in the shop?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh used to have to put them on hangers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you always hang them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I put them on a hanger and - had bars to put them on you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They were never left folded in the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you charge more for hanging?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 By - by law you could only charge by law the amount for the ticket. You un
derstand, by law, you see, but in some pawnbrokers business they charge what they call for}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 for hanging or - being placed, you see. But by law it was out of order. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about some of the people when you were a boy very young in the pawn bu
siness, tell me what you remember about them particularly, the types of people who brought in the clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh some - some of 'em were very nice people. Oh yes. There were - there were more nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about the very poor ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well the
y - they're poor, they're not - not nice you know. Yes, there was very poor people you see. Wages were very poor you must bear in mind. You see. They couldn't make the wage - wage pay, understand, you see. And some - sometime; they come across hard times,
 you understand, and there wasn't same social security in those days as there is today, you see. And - people had a lot of illness you understand happen in those days and came on hard times, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you ever have anyone who put the things in and r
eally wanted them back and you had to let them go without getting your money back or anything like that, did you ever have a lot of this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Let them - how do you mean let them have it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Suppose a woman brought her clothes in and then she couldn't af
ford to get them back, did you ever get them coming asking you to let them have them without the money or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, sometimes, yes. And - and sometimes I used to oblige them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were you ever let down or did they bring you the money later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well some let me down and some brought me the money later. I had for many years I used to - go - be - after - used be - they used to have a - a weeks holiday at one time. I used to go at the end of the week, Friday, I've come back from me ho
lidays on Friday and I've gone one - on - on Friday afternoon or Saturday morning and I've given one person ten pounds in silver to let it - let it out among my customers and pay me back on Monday when they pledge. I used to do that for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 A sort of a free loan?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were very soft hearted then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you see a great deal of poverty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, a lot a lot - a - lot of poverty but it was made through - some of 'em were respectable people I felt sorry for you underst
and and you see me being a Christian I couldn't deal with - you know, I was sorry for them, you understand, and I used to help them. See. I used to help them. A traveller came in - in - in my shop one day and a young girl came in about twenty-two, twenty-
t
hree and she said to me, she says, I've come to - this traveller just stepped at one side, he didn't go out of the shop, she says, I've come to spend a few pounds with you Mr Lindley, she says, you were very kind when me mother - when me mother when we wa
s young. And she spent about - she said, I've been saving up, she says, I've got the money and she spent about ten pounds with me in bedding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You sold bedding as well did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, oh yes. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you remember this family when the girl was young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh yes, yes, yes. And - you know, they - the - she - her mother live - for a - a big family you know and used to have to come and pledge you know and to pledge and this girl had grown up and got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  you know and her mother had passed away a
nd - she'd thought about me you know, the goodness I'd been to her I mean, in - in her younger days and - the man, he was a business man, whatsname, he said, my, he said, I've travelled in the trade, he says, and on business, he says, all over the world, 
he says, but I've never heard a bigger compliment paid to a man as that. That girl paid to you.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And she felt you'd helped the family when she was young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, yes. Come to spend this money with me she did, she - you was very kind to us when - to us mother when we were young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You used to lend them money without articles or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I just - you know, I've been - done best to help her, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Is there a trade union for pawnbrokers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Or a professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh yes, we - oh yes, it was a big - we'd a - we'd a - there's a good number of pawnbrokers in Bolton at one time, there were twenty - about - there about - going on for about thirty. And then - yes - we'd an association and then we'd a 
big association in London. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What sort of activities did they have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh we used to have our meetings and - and things - and business used to come up before us at the meetings you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were a man and growing up in a pawnshop did you feel there was a great division of interest among the workers in those days?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Can you tell me about it, what you felt it was, what the big division between the workers was? Was there a big division between trained craftsmen and other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well - you see - the working man in those days, you - you could - he'd come into your shop, you could have a foreign article, we'll say a foreign shirt and an English shirt, yet he were a trades union man, he'd buy - he'd buy the foreign shi
rt before he'd by the English one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - it was wrong to himself because he was buying the foreign shirt you understand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was the foreign shirt much cheaper?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Much cheaper, you see, it'd be one and elevenpence for the foreign shirt
 and the best English shirt would be half a crown, you see. Yet when he bought the foreign he were going himself harm. Because he were working in a mill as a - weaving the stuff to - to make - to make the best shirt and yet he'd buy the cheaper one.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Very studied wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Very stupid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you notice a big difference between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, big - a big}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786  difference,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  big difference in wages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What other things did you notice about them apart from the difference in wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well they - they were looked upon - they were looked upon, you know - as - if he wasn't a tradesman they looked upon as - as nothing, you understand. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was there a big difference in their homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Any thing else you notices - what would be the difference in their homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well I wouldn't notice you see in the homes you see. But - pawnbroking get a good name you know, with some people you know. They thought we were robbers you know. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And yet you worked hard to make a living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You had to work hard. It was a - the numbers you took in, you see, I used to - I used to take about - I used to lend }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 four}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  hundred and fifty pound of money about nine hundred pledges, it was hard work. All - all those things had to 
be packed away and - and ticket put on them and - packed away. See. There wasn't - wasn't easy going in a pawnbroking shop you know. Was - it was hard going. But - but - but I liked it. It -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You wouldn't have done anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I tell you if I had to live me life again I'd be a pawnbroker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
When you started work do you think it changed your attitude to life in any way? Did you suddenly feel grown up or anything like that, did it change your general attitude to life, becoming a worker?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well I - it did when I - I got me own place and me own boss. You see. But - it didn't alter any - any - anything in me mode of living you understand, I used to help people as much as I could. I rather give 'em a shilling than take a shilling off them.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This wasn't very good for a pawnbrokers shop though surely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, well I was always generous with people. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Before 1918 people used to divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 did you think of som
e people belonging to one social class and one belonging to another and can you tell me what the different social groups were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You didn't think some people were a different class to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well you - you - you'll always - you've had that all down the ages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
But before 1918 did you notice that some people seemed to be a different class to the others, did you think of some people being rough and some being respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They - they were more respectable a
nd better to get on - in - in - in my early life than what they are today. Everybody out for themselves today. More than what they were in those days. They used to give more help, neighbours used to get more help from one another. Not today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When your mother was ill or confined to bed did she get help from neighbours or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What would they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well they'd come and do the housework for them and - and do the washing and - and do the baking. But - but they're - they're not - 
not that way given today. Everybody's trying to get - not - knock one another down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You think they were much more Christian then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 More - more - oh yes, more }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 Christian}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have relatives living nearby when you were a child and how often did you see them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they're more clannish in - in those days than what they are today. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well I'd only aunts and uncles, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you see much of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, used see a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you come to each other's houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - I used to go and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 see me}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  grandmother. Me uncles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Would relatives come and visit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. No, it - I like the old days better than - than today. Oh yes. I - I think - what me father said on 
his deathbed that he's living in the - thank God he's living in England's best days, I - I - you know, I - I think they were - they were never - they were words were never altered what he said because England's never been good since his days you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you felt this applied especially to neighbourliness did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They all helped each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your mother have a lot of friends and where did she see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I - I can't say she'd a lot of friends. Well, she might 
have a lot of friends but she - she was more for the home, my mother. She was - she was more in the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your father have a lot of friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, not a lot. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have friends come to the house visiting a lot in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Not a big lot, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But you did have them occasionally?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they have to come by special invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well we had to - we had to make our - our own. We had to make our won amusements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your mum and dad go out visiting friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, not a big lot. No, my mother more - my mum were home birds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
When you had friends in, I know you used to have Sunday evenings singing as a family, but when you had friends in how did your parents amuse themselves with their friends, what did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh we - oh they had games and - and - we always used to have a part - every Sunday night after church we used to have my sister used to play the piano and - me brother the whatsname and we would sing - sing hymns and - and have - round the piano and sing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What happened when friends were in, what happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well we could - we could take any - bring - take any friends in we want.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Say you had mother and father's friends in what happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they're all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you make music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Yes. They're nowhere to go same as they had in these - in - in these days now because peoples off to bingo halls and one thing and another now of Sundays you know and - and dancing places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you had friends in did they have something to eat, were they asked to tea or did they just come in for the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh mother'd made them supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She'd always make them supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. We'd have a - a running buffet. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were you allowed to play games on Sundays or did your mother and father think it was wrong
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh we used to play games but didn't play for money or anything you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they allow you to play out in the street or did they think it was wrong to play games or work on Sunday, your mum and dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh we had - we played in the house, we didn't play outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have special clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh aye, we always had our - our Sunday best. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And then you had other clothes for school did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was your father interested in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did he ever talk about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was he never interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Never voted or took part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh he voted, oh aye, he voted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't remember your father talking about politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I - I think he was Conservative though because - I put up - I put up for the council you know, twice, in Bradford ward.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 get in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I didn't get in. It's a big Labour stronghold you know but I did - I polled very w
ell, I polled - I was only beaten about twenty. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't know why your father was Conservative, he never talked about why he held the views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he never - never talked much about politics.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your mother ever talk about politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was she interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No. No, I've been interested in politics, I - yes, all me life. I declared the winner here in - in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you put up for Labour you were twenty - what year would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Put up for Labour. I put up -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You put up for Conservative, you were only twenty you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Only twenty? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were only beaten by twenty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters as a whole, I know you were particularly close to one o
f your sisters, but how did you get on with the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh, not very good. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - you see, in families, you see - things didn't work out. You see, money matters, but I never let them up to hold me you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But as a child how did you get on with them, did you play altogether as brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well - I - I say - you see, me eldest brother and sister they - they were together, they clung and - and - I - me and the other sister clung together, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you not play together as children, did you play with neighbours children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - we didn't play a big lot. No, if we did we played in the back street but - we did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were you allowed to play with anyone who you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were there certain children you were told not to play - with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. Oh no, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Suppose somebody hit you, were you told to hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What games did you play as a child, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I used to play football a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were you allowed to get dirty and what happened if you did get dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh - we used get carry on to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Your mother used to play up steam did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you belong to any youth organisations as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I - I'm more interested in the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have any hobbies as a boy then, did you keep any pets or collect anything or do gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you spend your spare time, did you go fishing or for walks or bicycling or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Football a lot. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were always keen on sports were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. I - I was keen on sport - on footballing and running.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You never went walking or bicycling or fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, no, I was keen on running and - I was - treasurer the Bolton United Harries for thirteen years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you never go to theatres or concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. Never.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Or music halls while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you get any pocket money and tell me how much and what did you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Didn't you get any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I think I got sixpence I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 As a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember what you spent it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I've always been a saver.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you save it even as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you never buy sweets or anything with it or go to cinemas or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. I - I - I - I haven't been cinemas six times in me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you never remember buying sweets or toys with it or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No. No, I haven't been - I haven't been six times. I - I can't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You just went to see the Ten Commandments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And I went to one at -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What social class would you think you belonged to as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I - I belonged to the middle class. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Can you tell me what sort of people belonged to the middle class when you were a boy?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh there were good - good - good people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What sort of trades would come from the middle class do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 Oh well I would connect with a lot, some has been parsons and some's been - school - masters and - teachers.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who do you think the parsons mixed with when you were a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The parsons? Oh the parsons aren't same today as they were in my early days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who did they mix with socially when you were a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 The parsons? Oh they mix - mix with the working class - more so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about the teachers, who did they mix with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about shopkeepers, do you remember who they would mix with as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they'd mix with shopkeepers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What employers, do you remember who employers mixed with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, can't say that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Were you ever told to treat some people differently from others, did you ever call anyone sir, touch your cap to them or show respect in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who me? Oh yes, as a boy, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who were you told to do this to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh - there's people now I call sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But as a boy who were you told to call sir and touch your cap to, or madam, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh anybody in - in - in high - high position.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Such as - what type of high position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - an old - a man what's got a lot - such as these I sir to - Sir Walter Tongs, you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Would you come in contact with them as a boy though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Come in contact with 'em? I - I know Sir - Sir Walter Tong, he - he's practically - he's birthdays same - same day as mine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But as a boy would you know people like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who else would you have to touch your cap to or show respect to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I see Sir Walter Tong yet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was there anyon
e else you had to touch your cap to and call sir or any lady you had to call madam, do you remember anyone you were taught to look up to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well of course they've all passed on now you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But do you remember who they were when you were a boy that your mother taught you to show respect to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh, yes, there's plenty, this lady wrote me this letter. Mrs Bol - Mrs Bolovan. Oh there's plenty, there's plenty in the church. I - I think I've been blessed with knowing the people in the church what I work with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember anyone calling your father sir or your mother madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
When you - were a boy who were considered the most important people in the district where you lived and why were they considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh - remember the - the tax man, income tax man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was he considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 My father used to know him very well, John Ericson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And he was considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. He was - the income tax man.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember anyone else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And - oh aye, a man named - Webster, the timber merchant man, father used to deal - do business with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why were these people considered important, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well they were big business men and my father used to do business wit
h them and - with him being boss at the place he used to go and order timber, he could order what timber he wanted off him and - and they were friendly because it was - he'd give me father a tip at Christmas you know, three or four pounds, for having - su
pplied him with the orders you know, giving him the orders for the wood at - for; the works. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember anyone being referred to as a real lady or a real gentleman and why; do you think they were called this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh that - well it's - it's - how they lived, you know. And how they walked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How they walked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think they walked in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well, it have - you could tall a gentleman by his walk. Well I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How do you mean he held himself straight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes. How - how - how - everybody doesn't walk alike you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you think this was the difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember anyone called a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, plenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Who particularly and why was she called a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well it's - it's - the manner - and - how they - used to speak to people and how they - in a way like how they spoke, you understand. You see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you mean because they were very polite?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. YES? AND - there is people come 
across it to me - you - you're enlightened when they see them. I have people I meet in the street - after I've seen I was a different person altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 This was this Mrs Bradshaw you were telling me about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Mrs - Mrs Boller. She's such a nice lad
y it's - a very fine lady you understand, that - you were a different person after you spoke to her. There is - there is class of people like that. See. And yet - you feel better after you've had a word with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You think this is why they're a real lady or a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Yes. They - they inspire you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Where you lived as a boy did you feel that all the people in the working class or the lower class had the same standard of living or do you think there were different groups - different types?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh there's - there's some very good people among the lower class people you must bear in mind. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I'm talking about their standard of living, not just the people themselves. The labourers or the people who were just working for 
a living, would you notice a difference in the different types of them, would there be a division amongst them, some better than others even in the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh there's bound to be division between them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - it all - it all depe
nds on what - what - what position they had. See. You see, but you - you can come across some - some good living people among - in a very poor paid position you understand. You see, everybody's wants - they - they differ. Some peoples wants are very small
 and some people wants are very large, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Did you think of some people as rough though, when you were a boy in the shop did you think some people, were rough and others were respectable and did you notice the difference between them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes,
 well of course - that's according to bringing up. You see. You see, boys brought up in a - in a rough family and you know a poor district and he's -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Can you describe a rough family in a poor district as you saw it as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well - I - oh yes, w
ell you see - a poor family - it consists of the parents being rough - being ; being - well the marriage hasn't - worked, you see, and - and - they'd - they'd no control over their children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You saw this as a boy did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. You see, and you se
e, when a child - not loved by its parents you see it starts to go another way, you see, and - and they break away, and - and - they don't make - they don't care what they do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember any particular rough family when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I remember plenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were in the pawn shop when you were young before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Can you tell me about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What sort of home they would have, the actual description of the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh their home is - is terrible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well the place is untidy to start off with. You see. The mother's no interest in the home, father's no interest in the home and - and of course the children's brought up in the environment, you see, and they never - they never get
 out of it unless they come across somebody, if it's a boy he gets a - gets a girl as brings him out of that environment and it might be a - a girl you see. Some - some - some's given that way they can get out of it and some's that - as they can't get out
 of it. Because it's - they've never tried to get out of it. This - they seems all their life and they - they never alter they never make an effort to get out of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you think of some families as very respectable then and why was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well you see, it's - they - they'd have a different upbringing. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What did you think of as a boy as being a respectable family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think when you were a boy some people felt superior to others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh well of course you always get that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 As a boy do you remember it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
You see - it all depends on the position of any person gets. Some - they're swell headed if they get a good position and other - and some people that - not. It made no difference. There's plenty people says to me, my boy's got a good post.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In the pawnshop though do you think some people felt superior when you were a boy, some of your customers, do you think they felt }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 superior}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  to other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh some of 'em did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why do you think they felt superior?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well - it - it's rather peculiar - in our - in my shop we used to have divisions. You understand. The boards up you know and it just - like this - in a bank you know. At the counter you see. And the - the - the people - happen
ed about four divisions and these people what was - didn't want to be seen, they'd got in these - in these. The people as didn't - never bothered they'd come to the open counter. They wouldn't worry about being seen you see. And you see those people what 
goes in that - in those divisions was - they didn't want to be seen, you see, they wanted the - they felt - they felt like - super - a bit superior than the others, see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You thought there was a big difference between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think your father and mother had the same attitude to people in different classes or groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, my mother and father were all liked by people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think they felt the same about everyone though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a certain class or group?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh my mother was really grand parent, my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think your parents were class conscious at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 She liked - she - she liked - she liked all people - my mother liked all people. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And it didn't matter what they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It didn't matter how poor they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It made no difference, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think in those days when you were a boy it was possible to move up in the world and do you ever remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Move up? Oh aye, plenty moved up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How do you think they did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they - some of them did it by their own efforts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You mean hard work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Aye. Studying and - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember anyone particularly who did go up in the world?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I know plenty. I know plenty as went to school with me, one's - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 one
\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  a K.C. Member of Parliament and - and - 'course they've passed on now you know, they've died - they're - they're dead. Oh yes, I know plenty. But they di
d - they did off their own bat. Hard work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember anyone coming down in the world, do you think people came down in the world and do you remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, but it's been their own fault.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What happened, what brought them down do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Doing something they shouldn't have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Such as what?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I know teachers as have been - got in trouble and interfering with children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You went to church, do you think there was a difference in the people who we
nt to church and the people who went to chapel and what was the difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 People who went church and went chapel? I didn't see any difference. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't remember any difference at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I don't remember any - any difference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't think there were different classes went to church to people who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 None at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were a boy do you remember seeing a policeman round where you lived and what did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Seeing a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were you ever frightened and told, if your naughty I'll bring a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you never remember seeing any policeman as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't know how he treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about when you were in
 the pawnshop, do you remember seeing a policeman round and how do you think he treated the poorer people in the district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh for what I know he always treated them all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember seeing a policeman at all round the pawn shop when you were a boy, when you were first working, or even as a child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, notice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You didn't observe the police at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was your home rented, your home on Manchester road, your first home, was it rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Rented? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you ever see the landlord and what did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I can't - I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You never saw the landlord at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you ever think your father felt under any pressure to vote a certain way or anything when he was working for a firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, he were never pressed to vote a certain way, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Your father was never out of work and you didn't have a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You came with a silver spoon in your mouth didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What age did you start school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What? Day school or Sunday school. Day school? I tell you when I were five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What age did you leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you go a full day all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What kind of a school was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It was a Church of England day school. Pay fourpence a week. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was it a mixed school - girls and boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes, hundred in my class, they're bothering about forty today in a class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was there a hundred in a class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, hundred boys and hundred girls - fifty boys and fifty girls and you could hear a pin drop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What sort of discipline did you have - what were you punished for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well was - oh well, we didn't - we didn't get much punishments because - the teacher was more - you know, they was - childr
en were different in those days than what they are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were never punished, you never remember anyone being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No. No. No. Used to have a cane but - very - not - not very much used.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't remember what it was used for, if ever you got punished what it was for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh it - it was for doing something - playing tricks up in the school you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Were the girls punished as well as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Well they were - there wasn't much - there wasn't much punishment
 needed 'cos - we'd one of the finest headmasters there were and - they were better teachers - better teachers in those days than what they are today. The man was - he was a Harrow man as taught me - as my - yes, brought up at Harrow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did you like the teachers when you were at school, what did you think about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they - oh, they - they - they were far superior than what they are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You liked school did you or did you dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I didn't dislike school but I - I - I were never brilliant - brilliant, I could just hold me own, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But you still liked it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, I liked it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you go home to your dinner then in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I went home to me dinner there - there were no such - there was no dinners in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You didn't have dinners at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Do you remember what the teachers emphasised as important when you were a boy, such as manners or tidiness or punctuality or ways of speaking, do you remember what your teachers taught you was important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, it's too far back for me to think on that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You know you had good teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But you don't remember what they considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. Fine headmaster too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did your parents take an interest in school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they ever visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They never had any in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They didn't visit the school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did all the children come from the same type of home as you, in your school as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh, there were different - different ones, there's been brought up at my school, there's been parsons - been parsons been brought up - gone from the school and there's been M.P's and there's all types, solicitors. Been brought up at the school, where I'v
e gone. They've been brought up there and they've developed into the - the - these positions, M.P's, solicitors, barristers, professional foot-ballers
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you ever remember any children being left out of anything at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. How do you mean left out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No one was ever left out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't remember teachers singling any child out for special treatment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have gangs or groups in your school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you go on to another school after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. I finished my days there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I don't think I would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you do any evening school or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Have you any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you think you benefited from it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were in your teens and growing up you still continued your church didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were a very keen church person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you became a worker do you think your attitude to life changed at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I've been - I've been a church goer all me life, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Kept the same values?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you keep the same friends too? When you started to work in the pawnbrokers you still lived in the same district, did 
you keep the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, kept the same friends, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you start to go dancing or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, I never - no, no dancing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You told me you brought all your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Looking back on your life can you tell me in your own words your memory of Bolton before 1918 as a place and the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well they were grand people in - Bolton. A cotton town yes, and - oh I think life - life was better in those days than what they are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why do you think that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well, you see - they used to help one another. Today they're more selfish. Those days - used to help one another more and - more friendly. Yes. You see. You don't find it today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You thought they were good old days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why do you think they were good}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786  old }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 days apart }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 from}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 
neighbourliness}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 , there was a lot of poverty which you would see in a pawnbrokers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, but a lot of 'em have made their own poverty you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What about the people who couldn't help it, who didn't drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh there is some as couldn't help it. You see, that's where it was. Lot of people made their own poverty you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 know,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  there was - they was expensive living you know and - they - they - they never - provided for a rainy day you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you see a lot of this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh yes, lot of it. Yes. Of course you see - to me pawnbroking it got habitual with a lot of people. Yes. Always going, yes. You see. And - they lied going to the pawn - to the pawnshop you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I don't know, it - they felt more at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you helped them a lot you told me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you make a lot of friends of your customers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, I've - I made plenty of friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You would now families as families wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 With them constantly coming in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. I used to help them a lot you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In what ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well they used to come to me they was hard-up you know and - you see, and I used to try to help them what I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You're a very great Christian and this would play a great part in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Yes. I was - I was a very keen business man. I never let my people - my customers down. Wouldn't let them down, I always there - punctual. I've seen time when I've not been fit to go to my work and I've got there, you see, and if 
I've managed to get there I was all right, I could - you know, I wouldn't let them down. I thought they depended on me you see and I - I didn't like to let them down. Oh there's plenty hardships. But - some of 'em made it - made it - made their own hardsh
ips you know. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 you came to live here did you say?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh no. I didn't come to live here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You still lived in Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 I lived in Bolton, I - I lived on a place called }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 Crescent}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  Road there, lower down there, I first got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have to save hard to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well I - I've always been a saver, you see, and - I - I never got anything on hire. I had money - I - I'd always been a saver and I had money saved up, but things were different, they were c
heaper those days, I had about two hundred pounds saved up when I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 , you see, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you have a big wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I just - I wouldn't call it a big wedding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How long had you known your wife, did you have a long courtship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh - oh I'd know her, yes, I'd known her a good while. She came to my Sunday school do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you met her at Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh I - I think about - oh I think six or seven years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What changed in your marriage different to when you were a boy at home, did you come to a larger house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
I - I don't - no, oh no, we lived in a big house on the - on Manchester Road, you see, I couldn't afford to - I - it was - it wasn't small house but - we'd three rooms down - downstairs and three up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you still have a bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, we had a bathroom, yes, oh yes. I - I think I paid about fifteen shillings a week. Rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you ever see that landlord and what did you think of him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh the l
andlord - rent started to go up do you see and - there was a law - they had to give you so much notice. Before they could raise the rent. I think it was - I think it was three months notice. The landlord had to give his tenant three months notice he was g
o
ing to rise the rent. See? And the first - the lady - it was a lady that owned the house and - I wouldn't pay the advance. She come on and said, I - I said I wanted to go into law, must give me three months notice and then I - I'll come and pay the extra 
- the extra - go on the extra. And of course she - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 give}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  notice - notice to get out do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So she wasn't really a good landlady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. And - I - I eventually bought the house off her. You see. And - for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Your parents lent you the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did they help you set up home in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well I - I - well you see, I was very fortunate this way, I could go to the ware-house in Manchester with being in business and I used to buy my - cost price, you see and - until -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So they didn't have to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. And two hundred pounds went a good way in furniture in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was your wife a Bolton woman too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What trade was she, she wasn't in the pawnbroking was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. She was - she brought up as a milliner. But - her mother died young, you see, and her father got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  again and - she went in the mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh no. No. No, never worked after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did she like millinery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But not the mill?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 did you talk things over, like housekeeping and that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, yes. Yes, I'd only - I'd thirty-five shillings a week when I was first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 That was your wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. 'Cos it was - it was - it wa
s a - supposed to be a good wage that in those days, thirty-five shillings a week you know. You see. And - my father bought this business but he wasn't a pawnbroker because me father didn't know it you see. And - the only paid me a wage, what money - what
 
money was made went into the - see. No, no, they didn't tip all the money up. Yes. Oh yes, were a bit thing with children going out to working. When they was - you - you - my early time there was what they call half timers. In the mill, you could go half 
time at school and half time working in the mill. See. But it got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 stopped}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 do you see. You see, you could leave school at twelve and thirteen year - old in my time you know. Then it got to fourteen then it went - gone up to sixteen or seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were telling me as a boy you had a hundred children to a class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, in my - at the school I were brought up, Church of England school, was - was fifty girls and fifty boys in my class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And you all sat in rows did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 We had in long desk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You would think the discipline would have to be very strict for this wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, you see, you cold hear - hear a pin drop. 'Course the teachers were better in those days than what they are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why do you think this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well I - I 
don't think the teachers - well - I know a lot - a lot - I know several headmistress - headmasters you know and - high percent of the teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What do you remember particularly about your teachers that was much better, what do you think your teachers were better in or better at?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well - putting over, you see. And - they're better educated than what they are today. The teachers themselves, you see, them - a man that - our headmaster was finest headmaster that I - I knew a man, his name was Harry Di
vel. He brought up at Battersea - Battersea College. And - the man, Mr Price, Harrow man. You see, they're - they're - they were - people with good - good degrees you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was yours a very good school, was it in a very good district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No. Thickly populated you know. Yes. And - seven hundred scholars in it. No, the - the - were - they were - middle class people.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 It was a middle class school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. The - the church and the Roman Catholic wasn't - they were bitter against one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you see a lot of prejudice in Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes. In - in those days, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What forms did it take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You see. You see, you don't get that animosity today, you see, among the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How was the bitter ness between Roman Catholics and Protestants shown when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well I really couldn't ex - explain it, but - there was more apart than what they are today, you know. You see. It - all - it - always said in one time there could be - rows in Bolton, you know, Saturday night, drunken
 people and - and they used to send for the - the - the R.C. Priest and he could come and he'd }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 quieten}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 this - this crowd. He'd that much power over them. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In Bolton if someone did something wrong that the neighbours didn't approve of how; woul
d they show their disapproval, did they have any certain way of showing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
No, not - they weren't as bitter in those times as they are today. No. Not in - not in my days, no. No. No. No, they're more bitter today against people that does anything wrong but they - what they were in my day they were more sympathetic to them.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Kinder hearted you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Yes.
