\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. You see, it's altered. But that was more up in - up in East Lancashire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You didn't see it in Bolton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Not - not - no, not all in - no. No, there's more women working today than what there was in my younger days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You never had to repair shoes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No.
