 I had a brother and me - eldest - me eldest sister came at weekends. She used come - she used come and - and - make our dinner on Saturday and she used to stay and help us, you see, and - she'd make the tea of a Sat - or besides after dinner used to go -
 come and bring our dinner on a Saturday, mother used to send my dinner although I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 she used - used send my dinner and me sister used to - eldest sister would bring it then she used to stay at the shop and she used to make the tea for us. And she'd stay on 'til - seven o'clock - eight o'clock with us.
