\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, we - we used to play whist a lot, go to whist drives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You were both great card players?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And, in fact, I run them - I run the whist at the Harriers for thirteen years and made them seven - seven thousand pounds.
