\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, I run a whist -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How did your life change when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 , did you still live near your mum and dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Change? Oh no, I was - I was half - about half a mile away from my parents. It's all there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Your son didn't think you were fair to your wife, why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well he says - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 ought}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  to be going out of a Sun - sometimes we went go out of Sunday and it used to be - used to pick me up at the Sunday school at half past three and we'd go for a drive for about an hour - an hour and 
a half, two hours. He thought I - I should have a Sunday a month off and we should go off and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You and your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. And he - he'd have to take us you know, I couldn't drive the car.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How do you think your marriage changed from your mother
's and father's, do you think there were any changes in your generation from your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Changes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You don't think yours changed at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Apart from religion though do you not feel living conditions have improved }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 greatly}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  from what you saw as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh living - oh yes, they've improved, you see, but - people more selfish today you know than what - with my boy - my younger days you know. They - they - they don't like you getting on you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 But on the whole living conditions are better because for example no one had to pawn clothes nowadays do they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, but they're borrowing money. They go to the money lender now. And it's more expensive is that. See.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 You say they were thirty pawn shops in Bolton when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Oh yes, about - there'd be - oh well over - about - I should think about thirty-six in Bolton. There's none now today. No, they've all gone over to the money lender. You see. The man as bought my - I sold my place - I give it away to get rid of i
t, he was a money lender as bought it. And - when he bought it I - I promised to stay six month with him, money lending.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Why did pawnbroking get a bad name, I don't understand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No, you're looked upon by a class of people, if you're a pawnbroker you were nothing. You were making money, you know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Where did they get this idea from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
I can't tell you where you got the idea from you see. It never got a good name you see, yet we helped the poor people you see, now a money lender - they're getting about - forty - forty-eight percent. You see. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12537805\charrsid14639786 They - they lend 'em five or ten pound and they pay so much a week back and when they've paid about ten weeks, I got the knowledge of it through him being a money lender because he started the money lending
 to the customer who used to come - in the pawn, you understand, instead letting them pawn their things - he used to lend them money you see and - they'd borrow five pounds off him and he give 'em five pounds, they'd three and odd a week to pay back. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When 
they'd been paying about ten weeks he'd turn it over, you see, and - he'd lend them another five but he'd take - he'd take the balance out of what he'd left, you see, lend 'em five pound and you'd six pound five to pay back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you ever find in the e
arly days of pawnbroking that some people didn't have anything worth pawning and they'd be so poor they could come along and probably bring goods that weren't worth even pawning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, you got things as - as - very, very - you couldn't take in, you had to refuse 'em. See.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Then what would happen if you refused them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh they had to take them away. You see. But I was - I was very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 good}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786  to them, I - I understood them, you understand me you see, and that's why I did a good trade and - and - I used to try and lend them something on them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Even if the goods were no good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. You see. I used to try and lend them a bit of something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you find as a whole they honoured it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes, yes, they were - they were very sympathetic, most of them were. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 What did you particularly enjoy about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh meeting people. Yes. Different types of people, yes, and listening to their you know, their - how they lived. And you had to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you mean they would tell you how they lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 They would tell you about the hardships?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Their hardships and - you know - what they had to do to make ends meet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Tell me about some of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember any particularly, early on before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Well 
- my memories gone do you see, I can't remember the same now you know you see. They used to spend but they enjoyed themselves. Oh yes, in their own way. They had to make their own enjoyment, you see. And where you make your own enjoyment you enjoy better.
 You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Do you remember any individual case of hardship though from people who came in your shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh you see, it's going back too - too far back for me now you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Did you find that some pawnbrokers bullied them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 In what way would they bully them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
Well - they weren't civil to them you know, if they bought something in as wasn't - suitable they'd tell them to - happen swear at them and tell them to clear out. You see, well that wasn't my nature. You see. I used 
- sympathise with 'em and tell 'em I couldn't help them, see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Often in the case of some of them it must have been even money to eat they were trying to get mustn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 How old would you be when you stood for council?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Oh about twenty -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Was it before the 1918 war? What made you become Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Because I liked the policy. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 And yet your father didn't talk about his politics at all did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 No. No, he wasn't - a man. See.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 So you voted Labour that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes, I voted for him because I thought he was a good man. He got in all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3958973 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 When you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10176350 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
 did you still go to the Isle of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15819975\charrsid14639786 M}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 an for holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5247526 L  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 Yes. Went forty years run.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid3958973 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11471279\charrsid14639786 
\par }}